posting_body: ['Live, work, retreat.', 'Urban living in the apartment homes of Icon at Doyle in Emeryville.', 'CALL:', 'show contact info', 'x551', 'From $3,858', '.', '2 Bed 2.5 Bath .', '1290 Sq.Ft', '* Unit F - Available 08/17/22', 'Icon At Doyle', 'Website:', '<URL>', 'Address:', '5540 Doyle St Emeryville, CA 94608', 'Want more information?', '<URL>', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Join us for a self-guided or virtual tour!', 'Explore your new home from the comfort of your couch, or on a self-guided journey through our Neighborhood.', 'Live at the heart of creativity close to Berkeley, Oakland, San Francisco, and Silicon Valley.', 'Our urban apartment homes are located near restaurants and shops and feature high ceilings, fireplaces, and lots of windows to enjoy views of the Bay.', 'Custom made for loft-style living, our apartment homes feature stainless steel appliances, washer and dryers, and fireplaces.', 'Enjoy our fitness center at Icon at Park, assigned garage parking, controlled access, and walkable to Bay Street shopping.', '(Pricing and availability subject to change, plus additional costs for utilities and third-party maintenance services.)', 'FLOORPLAN/UNIT\u2002 \u2002FEATURES', 'Interior - Sky Light', 'LEASE\u2002\u2002TERMS', 'Variable', 'OFFICE\u2002 \u2002HOURS', 'Tuesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Wednesday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Thursday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Friday', '9:00am to 6:00pm', 'Saturday', '9:00am to 5:00pm', 'CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'x551', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'DISCLAIMER:', 'Call for details: pricing/availability subject to change at any time.']
